{
  "stem": "1419.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I have the book here if you want to see later on.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Then I can-- I have the book with me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We can look [INAUDIBLE] up the dates.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But it was-- I'm, I'm sure it was in 19-- in the beginning 1946 or the end of 1945.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Stanley, for those of us who were not there and who really don't understand the atmosphere in Poland, can you explain why, after the war, after so much suffering, this would have happened?",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know, but they hated the Jews is number one, and then the Jews came back, and they maybe want to claim their, their their, their real estate or whatever, their houses.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Property, property.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Property, their property.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Some of 'em were well to do, like the Lonek Lindenberger was one of the richest-- his father, one of-- one of the richest men in Nowy Targ.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the Ludwig Hertz I mentioned was the son of a attorney, who was quite well-- but no, he was a-- he was a doctor I think.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I think it was-- it was-- it was attorney-- were quite well to do.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They owned large pieces of property in city of Nowy Targ.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I guess they didn't want to see the Jews coming back and, and, and, and to live between, between them again and to claim the property.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I know that I came to my friends, to, to my neighbors, which I knew well.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were mine age, was going to school.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So the whole-- the first thing that they ask me, are you still alive?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[POLISH]?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Are you still alive?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They couldn't believe that I survived.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They thought they got-- they, they, they, they, they wished, maybe, that they killed all the Jews out.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
